<body>
  <header>
    <h1>How to Make a Will (Ontario)</h1>
    <div class="muted">A practical “law for dummies” guide: steps, rules, mistakes, and where to get help.</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#basics">Basics</a>
      <a href="#steps">Steps</a>
      <a href="#witness">Witness Rules</a>
      <a href="#mistakes">Common Mistakes</a>
      <a href="#help">Where to Get Help</a>
      <a href="#sources">Works Cited</a>
    </nav>
